{"lemma":"جَبَلٌ","slug":"جَبَلٌ","root":"ج.ب.ل","root_slug":"ج-ب-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ب-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَبَل","root":"جبل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":39},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4980"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mountain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mountains, mountain range"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to mold, to form, to shape, to fashion"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to knead"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to create"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَلَ (jabala) (form I); creation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَلَ (jabala) (form I); formation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَلَ (jabala) (form I); kneading"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Ugaritic 𐎂𐎁𐎍 (gbl), Biblical Hebrew גְּבוּל (gəḇūl, “border”)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.bal/","/d͡ʒa.ba.la/","/d͡ʒabl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4980","headword_ar":"جَبَلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any of the mountains"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awotaAd","text_ar":"اَوْتَاد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit. “pegs,” or “stakes,” a term applied to the mountains because they are supposed to make the earth firm, or fast,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the earth, that is great and long;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K;) or, as some say, only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is long;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) such as is isolated being called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamapN","text_ar":"اَكَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qun~apN","text_ar":"قُنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [and also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rocky tract; any rocky elevation, however little elevated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and sometimes it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rock;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] such, for instance, as is reached by the digger: and hence it is applied to Es-Safà and El-Marweh: (Mgh:) pl. [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAlN","text_ar":"جِبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and (of pauc., Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajobulN","text_ar":"اَجْبُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajobaAlN","text_ar":"اَجْبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who does not remove from his place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"you say of such a one,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa jabalN","text_ar":"هُوَ جَبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A niggard."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) [See 4.] ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief, of a people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their learned man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, K, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abonapu Aljabal","text_ar":"ابْنَةُ الجَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The serpent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) because it keeps to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabal","text_ar":"جَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune."},{"ki